3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep learning techniques to perform semantic labeling of remote sensing data, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics): The paper deals with processing and analyzing remote sensing data, which can be considered a form of computer graphics.
